Baltimore Ravens Beat Pittsburgh Steelers in NFL Opening Week

-- B y   D e x   M c L u s k e y
-- 
2011-09-11T20:07:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-11/baltimore-ravens-beat-pittsburgh-steelers-in-nfl-opening-week.html
The  Baltimore Ravens  beat the
Pittsburgh Steelers 35-7 in the opening week of the National
Football League regular season.  The win at M&T Bank Stadium in Baltimore ends a run of
seven straight losses for the Ravens against Pittsburgh with Ben
Roethlisberger starting as quarterback for the Steelers.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dex McLuskey at 
 dmcluskey@bloomberg.net  